parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent failure of the windshield wipers can cause reduced visibility during rainy or snowy conditions, increasing the risk of accidents, especially when driving at high speeds.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Paint delamination can compromise the structural integrity of the vehicle, potentially leading to windshield retention issues during impact, which can cause serious injury or fatalities.

windshield retention issues during impact (potential symptom).
